works.description: For the people believing in the eco-friendly approach, pedal power seems to be the first choice. While we were still in the route of welcoming the limited edition bicycles such as Vandeyk Contemporary Cycles, the Hublot “All Black” range or Damien Hirst’s bike for $500,000, the market is hit by awesome collaboration with “Livery Design Gruppe & Hurley.” Both the companies have teamed up to create the Phantom 4D Fixed Gear Bicycle.
